# Item 2: sintaxis F + Call [name] con forward reference
# Funcion add_eight modifica slot X sumando 8.
# Programa: X=50; Call [add_eight] (forward); ExitTop [X] -> exit 58
D 0 0 X Integer 50
D 0 0 Z Integer 0
D 0 0 Eight Integer 8
R 0 0 Call [add_eight]
R 0 0 ExitTop [X]
F 0 0 add_eight []
R 0 0 Add [X, Eight] X
R 0 0 Ret []
R 0 0 EndF
